15. List all files with the extension .txt in lorem folder.

"find . -name '*.txt'"

(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % ls
at.txt		at.txte		lorem.txt	sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % find . -name '*.txt'
./at.txt
./lorem.txt
./sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % 

16. Count the rows in sed.txt file from lorem folder. Look concatenate cat and wc with the pipe |.

"wc -l "file""

(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % ls
at.txt		at.txte		lorem.txt	sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % wc -l sed.txt
       9 sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % 

"cat sed.txt|wc -l sed.txt"

(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % ls
at.txt		at.txte		lorem.txt	sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % wc -l sed.txt
       9 sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % 
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % cat sed.txt|wc -l sed.txt
       9 sed.txt
(base) marina@MacBook-MacBook-Pro-de-Marina lorem % 

